<br>
BTW, he spawned on the 45th try and it wasn't even me that spawned him.  I was lining up for number 45 and someone else shouted they found him.  I did it a couple more times and got him again on number 49.  One of the downsides to multiple characters is that you need to repeat some of the more onerous quests for them.<br>
<br>
Yup, one of these will be for my monk -- 8th shawl ranks about 5th on my list overall for ideal monk shoulders due to hp and resists.  There are a few shoulders that are a lot better, but all of them are prohibitively difficult, rare, or desired by all classes (eg. Lendinara's quest shoulders, dracoliche's shoulders, etc.). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sakuta1>Sakuta1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/13/02 1:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=488.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yup, I finally got him</span><hr size=1> I'm not sure if this will help anyone, but when I did this part of the quest I also had a druid friend pulling the bunny trick.  Later I thought maybe it was not needed if you knew the trigger spots. One is dirrectly in front of the ramp and there is one on each side.  It really seems like more of a random which cup is the bean under trick, which also explains why some people get it first or second try and others after 46 trys.  I'm pretty sure it's just a lucky chance picking game. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eriseapyracheiristes>EriseaPyracheiristes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/19/02 12:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=488.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yup, I finally got him</span><hr size=1> Got him just yesterday; I'd s